```plantuml
@startuml staples-sparx_Wonko

participant "SparX Service" as SparX
participant "Kafka" as Kafka
participant "Wonko Core" as Wonko
participant "Alert Processor" as Alert
participant "PagerDuty" as PagerDuty
participant "Prometheus" as Prometheus

SparX -> Kafka: Publish events (via wonko-client)
Kafka -> Wonko: Consume events
Wonko -> Alert: Process events for alerts
alt Alert condition met
    Alert -> PagerDuty: Send notification
end
Wonko -> Prometheus: Expose metrics endpoint
Prometheus -> Wonko: Scrape metrics

@enduml
```